27 and delivery services and newborn care. Section 3.4 of this bill makes a
28 conforming change to indicate that the provisions of section 3.7 will be
29 administered in the same manner as the provisions of existing law governing
30 Medicaid. Section 68.3 of this bill requires the Director to submit to the United
31 States Secretary of Health and Human Services, to the extent that money is
32 available and as soon as practicable, a request to include under Medicaid a rate of
33 reimbursement of not more than $122 for such examinations and tests. Sections 3.7
34 and 68.3 authorize the Director to increase that rate of reimbursement to not more
35 than $150 on or after January 1, 2026.
